Package f_coupon.sys.core.dao.db Description

DAODB - Implements the DAO package interface in the DB using JDBC connection and SQL query. The DAO Package consist of interface Classes describing C.R.U.D (Create,Read,Update,Delete) actions,for Company ,Customer and Coupon
